    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? This car is an absolute dream and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been pampered its whole life and is in truly mint condition\u2014spotless inside and out. It drives like a charm and is just waiting for someone to take it on its next big adventure. Come see this beauty for yourself!",
