      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly have to see this beauty in person to believe it. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one\u2014it\u2019s been tucked away in my garage and still has that fresh, new-car smell! Not a single scratch or dent anywhere, and it drives like it just rolled off the lot. I\u2019m really sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Feel free to reach out if you want to take a look!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
