      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional E46 M3, a definitive example of high-revving, naturally aspirated precision. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS timing, delivering a linear power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline. This specimen features a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and the M Variable Differential Lock for optimal torque distribution. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach: the subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the rod bearings have been replaced\u2014addressing the critical S54 failure points. The chassis retains its factory-spec kinematics with no bushing deflection or hydraulic leaks. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the exterior retains its original depth with zero panel oxidation and all factory VIN tags intact. This is a collector-grade unit for the enthusiast who demands mechanical transparency and peak performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
